</div><div>我可以发送了。</div><div>&nbsp;</div><div>虽然是微薄的，但是</div><div>即使作为乃木坂46，作为我自己也</div><div>现在想自己能做的事</div><div>我想把它转移到行动上。</div><div>&nbsp;</div><div>然后，在灾区早一天</div><div>平静的日子回来了，</div><div>受灾的各位</div><div>希望能用笑容度过。</div><div>&nbsp;</div><div>&nbsp;</div><div>&nbsp;</div><div>山崎怜奈</div><div>&nbsp;</div><div>&nbsp;</div><div>&nbsp;</div><div>&nbsp;</div><div>&nbsp;</div>\t\t</div>","transTitle":"五年","url":"http://blog.nogizaka46.com/rena.yamazaki/smph/2016/03/030884.php"}